title: The Blue Rose complete season 1
description:
The Blue Rose is a New Zealand crime drama series, aired on TV3 in 2013. You can find individual episodes here and on other torrent sites, but I thought it'd make it easier for fans to be able to download the whole series in one go, rather than waiting for each episode to come in, which can take days as they're not seeded regularly. These aren't my rips, I merely compiled them to save others searching for, and waiting to download all 13 episodes.

Episode 2: What Difference Does It Make?
